extendedInfo.description: This app will allow you to browse photos and info on animals available for adoption right now at the Seattle Humane Society. When you locate an animal of interest, you can choose to email or phone the shelter to obtain more information as well as read more detailed info and view more photos via the web. Emails automatically include the SHS reference number and name of your selected animal so that there is no doubt who you're inquiring about. A fun, easy way to keep up on who's available including breed, size, sex, age, etc. and (unlike the SHS website) you can filter your searches by keywords in the animal's online data (i.e. just search "small male dogs" or "large female cats")Visit or donate to the Seattle Humane Society today if you can, but the app is FREE!
